	<h1 class="title">温暖的圣诞季，试试这 5 款与众不同的巧克力？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/img/missing_face.png" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">David Graver</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-12-13 07:15:51 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/18777/medium/18777.jpg?1449648187" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


